    year: '2012',
    title: 'First Steps',
    description: 'Started with modem unlocking experiments. Launched ModemUnlock4U on Blogspot—still live today.'
  },
  {
    year: '2015',
    title: 'First WordPress Site',
    description: 'Created Techuhow.com, a tech tutorial website. Learned WordPress, SEO, and website monetization.'
  },
  {
    year: '2018',
    title: 'Multilingual SEO',
    description: 'Launched DescargarAndroidApks.com with a partner. Gained deep experience in multilingual SEO and international markets.'
  },
  {
    year: '2019–2022',
    title: 'Affiliate & Automation',
    description: 'Built and scaled Locus010.nl, a Dutch Amazon affiliate site using automation. Multiple successful exits during this period.'
  },
  {
    year: '2024',
    title: 'Company Formation',
    description: 'Co-founded Mindjek Technologies LLP. Joined Phantom Rent A Car as SEO Specialist.'
  },
  {
    year: '2025–Present',
    title: 'AI-First Building',
    description: 'Building NoAutoRenew.com—a SaaS product using pure AI-assisted workflows. Continuing into 2026.'
  }
];

const principles = [
  {
    title: 'Results over theory',
    description: 'I focus on what actually moves metrics, not what sounds good in frameworks.'
  },
  {
    title: 'Long-term thinking',
    description: 'Quick wins are nice, but I prioritize strategies that compound over time.'
  },
  {
    title: 'Honest communication',
    description: 'I\'ll tell you what\'s working and what\'s not. No sugar-coating.'
  },
  {
    title: 'Continuous learning',
    description: 'The digital landscape changes constantly. I stay curious and adapt.'
  }
];
